data.description: Charming split level home boating a private 16x38 in-ground pool for warmer days, 40x15 attached shop with 10' door, 2 car garage, and raised garden beds! Great layout on the main floor includes a spacious main living room featuring a wood stove for chilly nights and three spacious bedrooms with a private ensuite in the owner's chambers. The gourmet kitchen has been updated entailing SS appliances, gas range, and a spacious deep sink. Potential mother in law suite on the lower floor featuring a single bedroom, bathroom, and spacious family room with exterior entry! [Home Energy Score = 4. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10220139]
